вҠў source
  yield text вүЎ Hello, how are you today?
  yield target_lang вүЎ Spanish

вҠў translate
  given sourceвҶ’text
  given sourceвҶ’target_lang
  yield translated
  вҲҙ Translate В«textВ» into В«target_langВ».

вҠў back_translate
  given translateвҶ’translated
  yield round_trip
  вҲҙ Translate В«translatedВ» back into English.
  вҠЁ round_trip preserves the meaning of the original text
